data.description: This popular Whitney floorplan features a spacious great room that flows openly into the dining area and kitchen, where there's a large a center island and pantry. The primary suite is located on the main floor with a private bath, double vanity, a walk-in shower, linen closet, and a generous sized walk-in closet. Upstairs is a large game room, the three secondary bedrooms and full hall bath. Additional home highlights and upgrades: 36" Dark brown kitchen cabinets, granite countertops and backsplash with a "Grey Chestnut" wood-look vinyl plank flooring in common areas. There is additional recessed can lights at great room, game room and primary bath. Also, cultured marble countertops and modern rectangular sinks in bathrooms, upgraded to second sink in hall bath. Out back you'll find a large 10x10 uncovered patio for entertaining guests. Schedule your showing today!
